<h3><b>The Allocation Model and Token Delivery Mechanics</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The RE Prime Sale operates on a </span><b>pro-rata over-subscription model</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">. This means your final token allocation is determined strictly by the ratio of your committed BNB relative to the total BNB deposited by all participants during the two-hour window.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Once the subscription pool closes, the distribution process follows a unique two-step delivery system:</span></p>
